com.facebook.buck.features.project.intellij

Class IjProjectTemplateDataPreparer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.features.project.intellij.IjProjectTemplateDataPreparer

  • public class IjProjectTemplateDataPreparer
extends Object
    Does the converting of abstract data structures to a format immediately consumable by the StringTemplate-based templates employed by IjProjectWriter. This is a separate class mainly for testing convenience.
